trans-unit.source: Represents an extension of a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.Workbook" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.Workbook" /> 对象的扩展。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IWorkbookExtension> interface defines a set of members that extend the functionality of <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.Workbook> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IWorkbookExtension>接口定义的一组扩展的功能的成员<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.Workbook>对象。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IWorkbookExtension> interface is implemented by the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.IWorkbookExtension>接口由实现<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase>类。

trans-unit.source: This is the base class for the generated `ThisWorkbook` class in document-level projects.
trans-unit.target: 这是生成基类`ThisWorkbook`文档级项目中的类。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Programming Document-Level Customizations](/visualstudio/vsto/programming-document-level-customizations.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[文档级自定义项编程](/visualstudio/vsto/programming-document-level-customizations.md)。

trans-unit.source: Returns an object that implements the <c>Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility</c> interface.
trans-unit.target: 返回实现 <c>Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility</c> 接口的对象。

trans-unit.source: An object that implements the <c>Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility</c> interface.
trans-unit.target: 实现 <c>Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility</c> 接口的对象。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.CreateRibbonExtensibilityObject%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的详细信息，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.CreateRibbonExtensibilityObject%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Ribbon.IRibbonExtension" /> objects that represent the **Ribbon (Visual Designer)** items to display in Excel at run time.
trans-unit.target: 返回 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Ribbon.IRibbonExtension" /> 对象的数组，这些对象表示要在运行时在 Excel 中显示的“功能区(可视化设计器)”项。

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Ribbon.IRibbonExtension" /> objects that represent the **Ribbon (Visual Designer)** items to display in Excel at run time.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Ribbon.IRibbonExtension" /> 对象的数组，这些对象表示要在运行时在 Excel 中显示的“功能区(可视化设计器)”项。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.CreateRibbonObjects%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的详细信息，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.CreateRibbonObjects%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: Called by the [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] to get an object that can be used by VBA code in the workbook that is associated with a document-level project.
trans-unit.target: 由 [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] 调用，用于获取可由与文档级项目相关联的工作簿中的 VBA 代码使用的对象。

trans-unit.source: An object in a document-level customization that can be used by VBA code in the workbook.
trans-unit.target: 文档级自定义项中的一个对象，可由工作簿中的 VBA 代码使用。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.GetAutomationObject%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的详细信息，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.GetAutomationObject%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: Called by the [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] to give developers an opportunity to reapply password protection to the workbook in a document-level project after the cached data has been saved.
trans-unit.target: 由 [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] 调用，使开发人员可以在保存缓存数据后在文档级项目中对工作簿重新应用密码保护。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.ProtectDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的详细信息，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.ProtectDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Guid" /> that identifies the <see langword="Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 一个标识 <see langword="Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility" /> 接口的 <see cref="T:System.Guid" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns an object that implements the <c>Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility</c> interface.
trans-unit.target: 返回实现 <c>Microsoft.Office.Core.IRibbonExtensibility</c> 接口的对象。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <see cref="M:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.RequestService(System.Guid)" />.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的更多信息，请参阅 <see cref="M:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.RequestService(System.Guid)" />。

trans-unit.source: Called by the [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] to give developers an opportunity to remove password protection from the workbook in a document-level project and enable cached data to be saved.
trans-unit.target: 由 [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)] 调用，使开发人员可以从文档级项目中的工作簿中删除密码保护并保存缓存数据。

trans-unit.source: For more information about this method, see <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.UnprotectDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 有关此方法的详细信息，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.WorkbookBase.UnprotectDocument%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。
